{
  "texts": [
    "A larger dataset could also provide more robust and comprehensive insights, reducing the potential impact of outliers or biases.",
    "Furthermore, human L2 writers come from diverse educational and cultural backgrounds, which influence their writing styles and vocabulary choices.",
    "The study may not have fully accounted for these individual differences, leading to potential biases in the results.",
    "Any biases or deficiencies in the data generated by ChatGPT-3.5 could affect the comparability between AI-generated and human-generated texts.",
    "For instance, half of the 30 essays generated by ChatGPT-3.5 did not meet the required 1,000-word which could impact the statistical derivation of keywords and collocation."
  ]
}